</P>
<P>
-- Britain' oil companies face a windfall tax on North Sea
operations which the Government hopes will raise up to 5 billion
pounds (8.3 Billion U.S. dollars)to finance sharply higher public
spending in the last three years of this Parliament.
</P>
<P>
Independent on Sunday:
</P>
<P>
-- Hundreds of thousands of small British children are
suffering brain damage from lead pollution, a report to be
published this week concludes. 
