<HEADLINE> PNA to Send Negotiation Team to Cairo </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, November 9 (Xinhua) -- The leadership of the
Palestinian National Authority (PNA) today decided to send the PNA
negotiation team to Cairo to work out a joint plan with other Arab
nations to face the hardline policy of Israel.
</P>
<P>
The decision was made when the Palestinian-Israeli Washington
peace talks held early this week yielded no progress because of
Israeli inflexibility.
</P>
