rankings, needed just 40 minutes to overpower Simon Frenz 9-1,
9-1, 9-0.
</P>
<P>
Graham Ryding secured Canada's winning point with a 9-7, 9-0,
9-2 win over Oliver Kowalski. Florian Possi then won a consolation
9-6, 9-5, 9-1 victory over Canada's number three Kelly Patrick.
</P>
<P>
In Group D, Malaysia scored a 2-1 win over Sweden while
Scotland breezed past Argentina 3-0. 
