<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, November 10 (Xinhua) -- The Philippine Department of
Agriculture is planning to import some 50,000 metric tons of white
corn at the request of the country's food producers, a senior food
official said today.
</P>
<P>
Addressing the National Food Congress' opening ceremony,
National Food Authority (NFA) Administrator Joemari Gerochi said
President Fidel Ramos is expected to approve the plan within the
week.
</P>
