<HEADLINE> Commonwealth Games Attract Fifty-six Participants </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, November 10 (Xinhua) -- A total of 56 countries
and regions had confirmed their participation in next September's
Commonwealth Games, reports said here on Monday.
</P>
<P>
The figure was revealed by Youth and Sports Ministry
parliamentary secretary Shahrizat Jalil in parliament. He added
that five million tickets had already been sold.
</P>
<P>
Some 6,000 athletes and officials are expected to take part in
the biggest-ever Commonwealth Games in Kuala Lumpur from September
11 to 21. 
</P>
