<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, November 10 (Xinhua)-- The world's largest payment
system Visa International is planning to capture the burgeoning
Indian market in a big way, Visa International sources said here
today.
</P>
<P>
India is one of the key countries for Visa and its products and
services and Visa will play a key role in leveraging fresh
opportunities offered by new market segments and emerging
technologies, they noted.
</P>
