first three quarters of 1997, the Beijing Customs Office has
reported.
</P>
<P>
Statistics from the office show that the trade volume of solely
foreign-funded companies totaled one billion U.S. dollars from
January to September this year, up 61.7 percent compared with the
same period last year.
</P>
