with Sampdoria on Sunday after clashes with Sampdoria's Fremch
defender Oumar Deng. Club doctor predicted a four week absence for
Casiraghi.
</P>
<P>
Both Casiraghi and Vieri have been in outstanding form for the
club and country.
</P>
<P>
Casiraghi has scored two and made two in his last three matches
for Lazio, while Vieri grabbed the vital away goal in Italy's draw
in Moscow. 
